# Commissions are generated from the strategy artifacts by build_commissions.py
# (the artifacts under strategies/ are the source of truth). Don't commit the
# generated copies: the skill commission would duplicate the 18KB SKILL.md and
# drift. Run `python build_commissions.py` to (re)create them.
strategies/*/*.commission.json

# uv build artifacts from testing the MCP server locally.
strategies/mcp/.venv/
strategies/mcp/uv.lock
